match_seo_description: [home_team_name] ukhombisa isimo esihle emasontweni ambalwa adlule, ngokuwina okumangalisayo nokuvikela okuqinile. Umugqa wabo wokuhlasela ubulokhu ubukhali, udala amathuba amaningi futhi usebenzisa amaphutha omphikisi. Ngaleso sikhathi, [away_team_name] uphinde wakhombisa ukumelana, elulama ezingqinambeni zokuqala futhi ehlela phezulu kwithebula. Abalandeli bangalindela amandla aphezulu, ukucindezela okunamandla, nokudlala okuhlelekile kuzo zombili izinhlangothi.
league_page_description: Hlola i-{leagueName}: Thola imidlalo ehleliwe yakamuva, imiphumela, izikhundla ezinemininingwane, nezindaba zeligi ephezulu yebhola likanobhutshuzwayo ku-{countryName}.
contact_us_page_description: Xhumana neqembu lokwesekwa kwe-Fanskor. Sithumele imibuzo yakho, impendulo, noma izicelo usebenzisa ifomu lethu lokuxhumana noma thola imininingwane yethu yokuxhumana lapha.
contact_us_seo_text: Lena indawo efanele yokufinyelela iqembu le-Fanskor! Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi unemibuzo, impendulo, izicelo zabalingani, noma udinga usizo nganoma yini, unganqikazi ukuxhumana nathi. Ukwaneliseka kwamakhasimende kuyinto ebaluleke kakhulu kithi, futhi sithembisa ukuphendula yonke imilayezo ngokushesha okukhulu. Ungasithumelela umlayezo oqondile usebenzisa ifomu elingezansi, noma uxhumane nathi usebenzisa imininingwane yethu.
contact_address_html:

contact_response_time_info: Sizama ukuphendula umlayezo wakho phakathi namahora angu-24.

faq_page_subtitle: Unemibuzo? Silapha ukuze sisize. Thola izimpendulo zemibuzo evame ukubuzwa ngezansi, noma sesha isihloko esithile.
faq_cant_find_answer_subtitle: Iqembu lethu lokwesekwa lihlala likulungele ukukusiza.
faq_page_description: Thola izimpendulo zemibuzo evame ukubuzwa nge-Fanskor. Funda kabanzi mayelana nezici zethu, idatha, nokuthi ungayisebenzisa kanjani kahle ipulatifomu yethu.
all_leagues_page_title: Onke Amaligi Ebholabhola & Izinkomishi | Thola Umqhudelwano Wakho Olithandayo
all_leagues_page_description: Hlola uhlu olubanzi lwamaligi ebholabhola nezinkomishi ezivela emhlabeni wonke. Thola imininingwane enemininingwane, izikhundla, imidlalo ehleliwe, nokuningi ngamaligi aphezulu nemiqhudelwano yamazwe ngamazwe.
leagues_page_seo_text: Siyakwamukela enhliziyweni yomhlaba webholabhola! Kuleli khasi, ungahlola wonke amaligi ebholabhola nezinkomishi ezivela emhlabeni wonke, kusukela kumaligi asendaweni athokozisayo kuya ezinkomishini zamazwe ngamazwe ezihlonishwa kakhulu. Thola kalula izikhundla zeqembu, imidlalo ehleliwe ezayo, nezibalo zomlando. Gxila ekuhlaziyweni okuningiliziwe kweligi yakho oyithandayo futhi uhlale uvuselelwe ngebholabhola. Thola uhlelo lwe-Fanskor lokuhlala unolwazi ngezindaba zebhola, izikolo ezibukhoma, nemiphumela. Ungaphuthelwa umzuzu webhola.
all_teams_page_title: Ibhola Likabulawo Iqembu Directory | Thola Iqembu Lakho Olithandayo
all_teams_page_description: Pheqa uhlu olubanzi lwamaqembu ebholabhola avela kumaligi athandwayo emhlabeni wonke. Thola imininingwane enemininingwane, amaqembu, imidlalo ehleliwe, nokuningi.
teams_page_seo_text: Hlola umhlahlandlela wethu ophelele wamaqembu ebholabhola ochwepheshe. Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi ulandela izingwe ezinkulu noma uthola izintandokazi ezintsha, thola lonke ulwazi oludingayo lapha. Sesha amaqembu, buka idatha yakamuva yokusebenza, futhi ugxile emhlabeni webhola leqembu.
football_teams_subtitle: Pheqa futhi useshe amaqembu avela emhlabeni wonke.

author_default_page_description: Hlangana nombhali ochwepheshe e-Fanskor, ohlinzeka ngezihloko zezemidlalo ezinokuqonda, izibikezelo, nokuhlaziya.
gdpr_default_page_description: Qonda ukuthi i-Fanskor ihambisana kanjani ne-GDPR futhi ivikela amalungelo akho obumfihlo.
privacy_policy_default_page_description: Funda Inqubomgomo Yemfihlo ye-Fanskor ukuze uqonde ukuthi siyihlanganisa kanjani, siyisebenzisa, futhi siyivikela kanjani idatha yakho ngenkathi ujabulela izikolo ezibukhoma, izibalo, nezibikezelo zomdlalo.
report_abuse_default_page_description: Ngabe ubone inkinga ku-Fanskor? Bika ukuhlukunyezwa ngokushesha futhi usisize sigcine umphakathi ophephile.
homepage_about_seo_text: Kwa-Fanskor, sikunikeza okungaphezu nje kwezikolo nezikhundla zeligi yaseTurkey i-Süper Lig, kuvuselelwa njalo ngesikhathi sangempela. Uma nje umdlalo uqala, sikunikeza ukubuka konke komdlalo okubanzi kakhulu nezikolo ezibukhoma, ngakho-ke nge-Fanskor uhlala unolwazi nge-Süper Lig yaseTurkey! Sinikeza ukuhlaziya okuningiliziwe nezibalo zeqembu, kanye nezibuyekezo ezibukhoma zokuhlanganisa yonke inhloso noma ezinye izikhathi ezibalulekile. Uhlela kusengaphambili? Thola kalula mayelana nemidlalo ezayo futhi ungalokothi uphuthelwe umdlalo obalulekile futhi. Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi ulandela iqembu lakho olithandayo noma ulandela yonke imidlalo yeligi, i-Fanskor ikunikeza isithombe esihle kakhulu, esiphelele, esithembekile, nesinamandla sebhola likabulawo laseTurkey ngokukhetha komlandeli wangempela. Ungabi nje umgadi womdlalo, kodwa ube umshintshi womdlalo nge-Fanskor. Thola ukuhlanganisa kwakamuva, okudumile, nokuphelele manje!
sidebar_about_seo_text: Kungakhathaliseki ukuthi ulandela amaderby athokozisayo noma izindaba zangaphandle ezingalindelekile, i-Fanskor ikulethela izindaba zakamuva nokuhlaziya. I-Fanskor iyisitolo sakho esisodwa sezindaba ze-Turkey Süper Lig. Ungahlola imidlalo ehleliwe, ubuke izikhundla zakamuva, ulandele izikolo ezibukhoma, futhi ufinyelele zonke izibalo zeqembu ngqo ephaketheni lakho.

match_page_title: {homeTeam} vs. {awayTeam} - Isikolo Esiphilayo, Ukubikezelwa & Izibalo Zomdlalo | {leagueName}
match_page_description: Zilungiselele umbango oshukumisayo phakathi kwe-{homeTeam} ne-{awayTeam}, uthembisa ukuncintisana okukhulu nezikhathi ezijabulisayo kubathandi bebhola! Njengoba lawa maqembu amabili engena enkundleni, wonke amehlo azobe ekuqeqesheni kwabo, ekusebenzeni kwabadlali, namasu abawasebenzisayo ukuze baqinisekise amaphuzu abalulekile.
match_page_h2h_seo_text: Ngokomlando, izihlangano phakathi kwe-{homeTeam} ne-{awayTeam} bezilokhu zisondele, ngemiphumela emincane nedrama yomzuzu wokugcina. Izibalo ezinemininingwane njengephesenti lokubamba ibhola, ukushaya amagoli, nokunemba kwephasi kuzovuselelwa ngesikhathi sangempela, kukuvumela ukuthi ulandele yonke imizuzu ebalulekile.
match_page_standings_seo_text: Bheka umugqa oqinile ophakathi we-{homeTeam} nomshayi magoli wabo oyinkanyezi, bobabili ababalulekile ekuphazamiseni abavikeli. I-{awayTeam}, ngakolunye uhlangothi, incike kakhulu ekuhlanganiseni kwayo okunamandla kwabavikeli abaphakathi nabadlali abasheshayo, abangashintsha inkambo yomdlalo nganoma isiphi isikhathi.
match_page_activity_seo_text: I-Fanskor inikeza izibuyekezo ezibukhoma ezinkundleni, izikolo zesikhathi sangempela, nezibalo zomdlalo ezinemininingwane. Kusukela ekuhlaziyweni kwecebo kuya ezazisweni zamagoli zesikhathi sangempela, ngeke uphuthelwe noma yimuphi umzuzu obalulekile. Hlanganyela ebumnandini, yabelana ngezibikezelo zakho, futhi uvumele injabulo ikudle njengoba i-{homeTeam} ne-{awayTeam} zilwela ukubusa.
